longBusinessSummary: GCM Resources Plc operates as a resource exploration and development company. It primarily develops the Phulbari coal and power project that relates to thermal coal and semi-soft coking coal located in Bangladesh. GCM Resources Plc was incorporated in 2003 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
